            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Hd1e108">Rubrica 9</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Hd1e111">De amicis leuibus verbalibus fictis et non veris</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>¶ De amicis leuibus verbalibus fi
               <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>ctis et non veris. Rubrica. 9
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e118">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e117">SAlomon in prouerbiis. c.
      <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>14.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e124">Etiam pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="75" break="no"/>ximo suo pauper odiosus erit: amici
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>vero diuitum multi.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e132">
               <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e134">Aristoteles ethicorum libro 8. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e136">In tyrannide.
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>nihil vel parum amicitie est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e142"> /
      <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e145">Lib. 9. c. 13. et
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e144">Fit prauorum amicitia mala: communicant
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>enim prauis instabiles entes: et mali autem
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>fiunt assimulati adinuicem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e155"> /
      <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e160">Idem de ma
        <lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>gnorum moralium li. 2. c. 62.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e157">Secundum conferens
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>amicitia non firma est: sed cum conferente muta
        <lb ed="#V" n="84" break="no"/>tur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e167"> /
      <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e175">Idem <sic>rethorice</sic> li i. c. 20.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e169">Apparens
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>amicus adulator est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e175">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e190">Tullius de amicitia:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e179">Utilitates quidem
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>etiam ab his percipiuntur sepe qui simulatio
        <lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>ne amicitie coluntur et obseruantur temporis causa.
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>In vita tyrannorum nulla fides: nulla charitas
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>nulla stabilitas beniuolentie potest esse fidu<!--108.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="41-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1" break="no"/><sic>ducia.</sic> Omnia semper suspecta atque sollicita:
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>nullus locus amicitie. Quis enim eum aut di
        <lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>ligit quem metuit: aut eum a quo se metui pute
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>tur: coluntur tamen simulatione amicicie dum
        <lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>taxat ad tempus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e209">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e227">Ouidius de ponto li. 2 epistola. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e213">Turpe qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>dem dictu: sed si modo vera fatemur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>Uulgus amicicias: vtilitate probat.
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>Illud amicicie quondam venerabile nomen
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>Prostat: et inquestum: pro meretrice sedet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e225">
               <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e245">Quintilianus declamationum. i. declam.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e229">Cum propter pecuniam ames idem amoris et spei
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>finis est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e237"> /
      <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e257">15 declam.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e239">Nescis an diligat:
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>cuius non habet experimenta nisi sola felicitas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e246">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e269">Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum li. 3. e. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e250">Errat qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>amicum in atrio quirit: in conuiuio probat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e256">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e281">Auctor lib. de for. honeste vite. ca. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e260">Nul
        <lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>lius per assentationem amiciciam merearis.
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>Nec hanc promerendi a te aditum aliis pandas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e268">
               <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e295">Cato. ca. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e272">Qui simulat verbis: nec corde
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>est fidus amicus: Tum quoque fac simile: sic
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>ars deluditur arte.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e280">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e309">Cassiodorus de amicitia. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e284">Uix inuenitur di
        <lb ed="#V" n="24" break="no"/>lectio quae non sit questuaria et venalis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e290"> /
      <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e319">16.
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e292">Qui simulatorie amat: in prosperis amat
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>amicus: aduersarius in aduersis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e300">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e335">Auctor li. qui dicitur facetus. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e304">Sed tantum in
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>mundo: modo non est fidus amicus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>Fraude est etenim callidus omnis homo.
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>Sed qui non potuit socium: sibi querere sidum:
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>Diligat hic alios sicut amatus erit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e317">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e353">Gualterius de castellione li. 9. et pe.</ref>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e325">
               <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e329">/ Testatur eorum
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>Finis: amicicias regum non esse perhennes</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e335">
               <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e370">Heinricus samariensis lib. i. parte. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e339">Deli
        <lb ed="#V" n="36" break="no"/>cias veris sequitur: sed tempora bruine.
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>Deserit ablato remige falsus amor.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e347">
               <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e384">Bertrandus iconomica. c. 12.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e351">De verbis magna est copia amicorum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e357">
               <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>
               / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e395">Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 34.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e361">Tempore
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>felici: multi dicuntur amici.
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>Tollere qui cupiunt: et dare nulla volunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-d1e369">
               <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Rd1e410">Prouerb.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d31016-Qd1e373">vulgar: Retie lamigo to colue</quote><!--add "(30 so." to line below?-->
            </p>
         </div>
